snippet.title: Bad Bots Rises - Trailer
snippet.description:
An unknown ship attacked earth. The streets are now crawling with bad robots. Get yourself a weapon and clear our lands off of metal invaders.

Bad Bots Rises is now on itch.io! Visit the link below to learn more.
